####  Bench #####

bench get-app repo_link.git --branch branch-name
		- install app from github

bench new-site your-site-name
		- Create a new site

bench --site your-site-name list-apps
		- list-app in site

bench --site your-site-name backup
		- backup database & files of site

bench --site your-site-name backup --with-files
		- take backup of site with files public & private

bench --site trademode.com restore location_path/db.sql
		- restore database

bench --site your-site-name set-admin-password new-password
		- reset Administrator password

bench --site your-site-name add-to-hosts
		- add site to 127.0.0.1 (Multitanancy Mode)

bench --site trademode.wrok reinstall
		- to reinstall the site


